Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.32,0:34:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Takes me about 24 hours to find\Nemployment in any town I've ever been
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.07,0:35:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in. That's if I'm slow.\NI not only had jobs when unemployment
