Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.20,0:41:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or pretty your hair\Nor swirl your skirts. All those things
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.31,0:41:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to bring you happy make you\Nhappy.
